OL,3,CGuernsey fisherman concerned about
OL,4,Cfalling numbers of local crabs
OL,6,FA Guernsey fisher has expressed his
OL,7,Fconcern over the decline in brown
OL,8,Fcrabs in Channel Island waters.
OL,10,FThe decrease has been attributed to
OL,11,Fwarmer water temperatures, scallop
OL,12,Ffishing, dredging and a rise in some
OL,13,Foctopus species in the Channel Islands.
OL,15,FClive Brown, who has been crabbing in
OL,16,FGuernsey since he was a teenager, told
OL,17,FITV News: "This has come on quite
OL,18,Fquickly, this lack of crab."
