OL,3,CGuernsey fisherman concerned about
OL,4,Cfalling numbers of local crabs
OL,6,FHe added: "Obviously we've had our
OL,7,Flobster season this year. We've had
OL,8,Four crab season during the winter, not
OL,9,Fspectacular but ok. Again, lobster
OL,10,Fseason, not spectacular but ok. And we
OL,11,Fgo into our summer crab fishery and
OL,12,Fit's just died."
OL,14,FClive says "almost industrial-level"
OL,15,Fscallop fishing is having a
OL,16,F"detrimental effect" on the number of
OL,17,Fbrown crabs in Guernsey waters.
