OL,3,CGuernsey fisherman concerned about
OL,4,Cfalling numbers of local crabs
OL,6,FIn 2021 a team from Jersey Marine
OL,7,FResources started a tagging survey to
OL,8,Ftry and identify why the brown crab
OL,9,Fpopulation was declining.
OL,11,FMarine ecologist Dr Samantha Blampied
OL,12,Fsays many of the crabs have headed
OL,13,Fwest into deeper waters and the drop
OL,14,Fin numbers is not necessarily an
OL,15,Fimmediate cause for concern.
