OL,3,CGuernsey fisherman concerned about
OL,4,Cfalling numbers of local crabs
OL,6,FShe said: "Probably there will become
OL,7,Fa point where the population will be
OL,8,Fat a critical threshold for where they
OL,9,Fcan continue to reproduce but I think
OL,10,Fit'll be a long time before we get to
OL,11,Fzero crabs."
OL,13,FSamantha says that while around 500
OL,14,Ftonnes of brown crab were caught in
OL,15,F2012, less than 100 tonnes per year
OL,16,Fhave been reeled in more recently.
